These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
2 different games are played: poker, whist
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, dahlia
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: country, reggae
There are 2 different favourite colors: turquise, lavender
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
2. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
3. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Game      | whist      | poker    |
| Flower           | dahlia | marigold |
| Music-Genre   | country       | reggae  |
| Color     | turquise      | lavender     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, pakistani
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, vegafina
2 different games are played: domino, canasta
House: colonial, cape-cod
1. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
2. the pakistani is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
3. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Nationality          | pakistani | egyptian |
| Cigar   | dunhill       | vegafina         |
| Game           | canasta     | domino         |
| House     | cape-cod    | colonial    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
City: venice, berlin
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, water-polo
There 2 different types of food: blueberry, artichoke
2 different games are played: whist, canasta
1. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
4. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| City         | berlin          | venice |
| Sport           | water-polo | badminton     |
| Food   | blueberry            | artichoke         |
| Game     | canasta         | whist   |

