2. the townhouse house is the indian##1
3. the craftsman house is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| House      | townhouse     | craftsman   |
| Hobby   | fishing    | chess |
| Food   | cabbage   | apricot |
| Nationality           | indian | mexican    |

