1. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
2. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
