2. the person who likes pink is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person playing go##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |
| Pet         | goldfish    | rat  |
| Color           | purple      | pink |
| Game   | backgammon      | go   |
| Transport         | bike | bus    |

