.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, chef
2 different games are played: chess, whist
There are 2 different favourite colors: amber, brown
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, bolivar
1. the person who likes brown is on the left of the fisherman##1
2. the person playing chess is the person who likes amber##1
3. the person who likes amber is the bolivar-smoker##1
4. the game-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Job      | chef     | fisherman |
| Game          | whist   | chess |
| Color   | brown     | amber     |
| Cigar     | game | bolivar     |

 